sentences.en: The oldest extant document is dated 1492.
sentences.cn: 现存最古老的文件追溯到1492年。

sentences.en: The body of extant scholarship on Griffith was so tiny that it could all be read in a day.
sentences.cn: 现存的关于格里菲斯的学术论文太少了，一天之内就能读完。

sentences.en: A medieval manuscript called L contains all eighteen extant tragedies by the Greek playwright Euripides.
sentences.cn: 一份名为 L 的中世纪手稿包含了希腊剧作家欧里庇得斯所有现存的十八部悲剧。
